Rating: 2
As is this recipe is pretty good. It was a nice side dish for my pork loin with peach mustard sauce. I find though when using mustard seeds the flavor of your dish will go from good to Zowie just by toasting the mustard seeds until they pop a little. They next time I make this I will add more mustard seeds and toast them.

